reviews.comment: Brought my family here, it was very busy when we got there so getting our food took some time. The sandwiches were amazing. We ate outside on the patio while listening to a guy that played music and sang on the patio. Perfect place to go and relax with a bottle of wine and eat lunch. I used to go here years ago a lot, Was almost 10 yrs, glad I went back. I will be sure to revisit more often again.
